      "content": "<p>Title:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BSc (Hons) Business Management with International Business</li>\n<li>BSc (Hons) Business Management with Marketing</li>\n<li>BSc (Hons) Business Management with International Finance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\">SCQF Level: </a><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\">9 (Bachelors) or 10 (Honours)</a><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\"> </a></p>\n<p>Mode of delivery and duration: Fast Track, 18-42 months</p>\n<p>Language of delivery: English</p>"
